reviews.review_text: st steeephen! well, you know how good the show is and you can imagine how not-so-good the sound is, but I'm really digging the crowd reaction to the St Stephen jam in Greatest Story around 3:40 right now...

Oh my gosh stop clapping along! The sound on this one is pretty decent, but the entire stadium seems to clap during every song.  I know, if you were there it sounds like the place is on fire, but I mean they don't stop clapping.  China>Rider? Forget about hearing the band through the thunderous rhythmic clapping.  I put on BTW thinking oh a slow one so I'll hear the band.  Nope, just slower rhythmic clapping.  I can't listen, which is a shame.
- Recording is unlistenable, sadly. Great show.
